{"id": "1275098503340884009", "channel_id": "1275098503340884009", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "> 大家好，這裡是難忘今宵攻略組，本期為大家帶來的是第15期「融災禁區」地圖。\n\n圖一：地圖\n圖二：時靈擺\n圖三：第4波時靈擺效果預覽\n◆每兩週刷新獎勵與關卡，每個關卡只需要完成普通模式、困難或癲狂模式其中之一。\n\n◆經過毒地板（紫色格子）時，會扣除 血量上限 的約5%，也就是固定值。\n\n當踏入毒地板所扣除的血量被判定為致命傷害，則觸發死亡抵抗/復活確認。\n\n◆同一關卡的各級警示地圖都相同。\n\n▼▼▼\n\n【第1波】特遣紀錄 - 索蕾爾「薔薇禮贊」- 【卵】地圖\n【第2波】無光之境 - 間隙 地圖【混沌2，深海8，血肉6，超維4】\n【第3波】特遣紀錄 - 索蕾爾「薔薇禮贊」-【紅色慶典】地圖\n【第4波】特遣紀錄 - 莉莉「故事的魔法」-【最懷念的人】地圖\n【第5波】意識潛遊 - 尤烏哈希「血與沙」-【悲劇的謝幕】地圖", "timestamp": "2024-08-19T14:26:13.381000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1275098506654126222", "filename": "15low.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2874589, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1275098503340884009/1275098506654126222/15low.jpg?ex=69fb4f86&is=69f9fe06&hm=6b901f3e15fce827670ba95d9d48f474c2fbfb499415082cb987749e0936b0d0&"}, {"id": "1275098507807817778", "filename": "15.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1963578, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1275098503340884009/1275098507807817778/15.jpg?ex=69fb4f86&is=69f9fe06&hm=932d32913af5fc58ce3f6465f586cdd6a5933fe25a96cc3ea925238c903738e3&"}, {"id": "1275098508210475069", "filename": "2d48e310ebf86ad6.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 491140, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1275098503340884009/1275098508210475069/2d48e310ebf86ad6.jpg?ex=69fb4f86&is=69f9fe06&hm=eb5275b0e61c7b5b30708f532ee8d9d780817cc8c9e175d720ca0ca425d68fe9&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1275098503340884009", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關卡地圖「融災禁區」總覽ⅩⅤ", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1283686881858420777", "1181143392739147778"]}
